contentrichtext.text: {{wiktionary|planetary}} '''Planetary''' means relating to a [[planet]] or planets. It can also refer to: * [[Planetary (comics)|''Planetary'' (comics)]], a comic book series by Warren Ellis and John Cassaday * [[Planetary habitability]], the measure of an astronomical body's potential to develop and sustain life * [[Planetary nebula]], an astronomical object * [[Epicyclic gearing]] (planetary gearing), an automotive transmission technology * ''[[Planetary Radio]]'', a public radio show about space exploration, produced by [[The Planetary Society]] * [[The Planetary Society]], the Earth's largest space interest group * [[Planetary (rapper)]], one half of east coast rap group [[OuterSpace]] * [[Planetary (Go!)|"Planetary" (Go!)]], a 2011 song by rock band My Chemical Romance * [[Planetary scanner]] - type of image scanner for making scans of rare books with mounted camera taking photos {{disambiguation}}
